def leapfrog(A, u, v, h, N):
    """Leapfrog finite difference scheme."""
    v = v - h/2 * A @ u
    for i in range(N-1):
        u = u + h * v
        v = v - h * A @ u

    u = u + h * v
    v = v - h/2 * A @ u

    return u, v
